 stews in Castilla y Le\u00c3\u00b3n.", "Japanese cuisine is celebrated for its precision, seasonal ingredients, and umami flavors, featuring sushi, ramen, and tempura. Washoku, the traditional Japanese meal format, is recognized by UNESCO as intangible cultural heritage."], "scores": [0.8052913055761763, 0.6675147024745782, 0.6325817358385178, 0.6286868038183971, 0.6086269127558301], "model_name": "bge-base", "document_ids": ["Italian", "Greek", "Chinese", "Spanish", "Japanese"]}}